window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>January 2043. The Vogthar Horde has come, and they bring real death with them. Not even players are safe from the power of Malware Blades....</p> <p>Worse, the Realm of Order, dominion of the Overmind Sophia, is in danger - slowly being corrupted by an ancient evil, the Lich Priest. And if he is successful, it could mean the end of Sophia and the downfall of the Crimson Alliance. </p> <p>Grim Jack never thought heâ€™d find himself siding with the Empire, but now that this terrible new threat has arrived, making friends of old enemies may be the only way to survive. </p>"; 
